*
Consent Requirement:
You may not sell, distribute, or otherwise use TacticalPad-generated content (e.g., images, videos) for commercial purposes without prior written consent from Temma Software.
*
Prohibition of Use for Promotion of Other Software or Apps:
You may not use TacticalPad's name, image, or any TacticalPad-generated content to promote any other software, application, or service without written permission.
